item.title: By: Judith & Matt
item.dc:creator: Judith & Matt
item.description: <p>What a difference! incredible... very nice whats the thing under your temple??? is it for you to sit on like a gnome??!! when's the BBQ and few drinks then...we'll come! enjoy your view don't forget the GPS to find your way back! My bro's a computer geek...and has way too much money it's not fair!! Keep dreaming Simon one day in your mansion with Fi.</p>
